node.text: Don’t talk to me or my son ever again... unless it’s about AMC+ and their incredible lineup of epic world shows that help keep my vibes spooky all year long... shows like A Discovery Of Witches, The Watch & The Walking Dead season 10! Start your one-week free trial of @amcplus today! Binge #TheWalkingDead Season 10 to see Michonne’s final episode, the epic conclusion to the Whisperer War, and the recent 6 stand-alone stories. #ad

node.text: I haven’t had a haircut in months & have been feeling so unkempt, not-handsome & caveman-like during these months of isolation, BUT... while partnering with @dollarshaveclub for their #MenGetReal campaign, I decided that even though there’s seemingly not much of a reason to shave or look presentable, that i’d give it a try anyways! In an attempt to look and feel more human at this time, I tried my best to give myself a little isolation self-care-makeover :) it’s just for me of course... but it makes me feel a little bit better, and that’s worth something! Dollar Shave Club’s got all your grooming needs covered, now at a store near you! #ad #DollarShaveClub

node.text: So deeply excited and insanely thrilled to be launching this podcast today with my dear friend @andrewsiwicki! :.-) link in bio and I hope that you will check out the first episode of “Sweet Boys” because it’s going to be such a wonderful, fun positive place to come every week for just good vibes, laughter and fun 💕

node.text:
This photo 100% makes me look like the author of a book called “The Joys Of Gem Collecting” or something like that... but I like it and I hope you do too 💎 

Also, If you’re reading this, I hope you are mentally and physically well and managing to remain calm, cool, and collected at this strange time in the world 💕

node.text: I tried to take a cute pic with this beautiful baby deer in Japan and & instead he just started eating his own ass. I just rolled with it. Can’t believe he did that to me but i’ve still got mad respect for this adorable troll.
